main event: A UFO sighting was reported over Washington Island, Wisconsin on June 24, 1965, involving two objects observed by a civilian.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for approximately 5 minutes,The objects were described as emitting bright white light,An eyewitness discussed the possibility of light rays bending over water as an explanation,The sighting was reported to the Coast Guard, and they searched for evidence but found none,The report included sketches and maps for further evaluation.
sighted object: two unidentified flying objects emitting bright white light
witness description: Civilian who provided detailed observations and sketches
